2002-1987 (La. 10/25/02)

Patsy HARTLEY v. PHYSICIANS MUTUAL INSURANCE COMPANY, et al. No. 2002-CC-1987. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re Physicians Mutual Insurance Company; — Defendant; Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs, Parish of Concordia, 7th Judicial District Court Div. A, No. 36,502 A; to the Court of, Appeal, Third Circuit, No. CW 02-00556.
